modules.description: Provides functions for generating random test cases and validating properties using a custom generator and checker. Operates on arbitrary data types, including lists, options, and custom variants. Integrates with Alcotest to run property-based tests with randomized inputs.

Converts QCheck tests into Alcotest test cases with customizable output, verbosity, and test speed. Operates on QCheck2.Test.t and Alcotest.test_case types, supporting detailed failure debugging and random seed control. Used to integrate property-based testing with Alcotest's reporting and execution framework.
